trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> control in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de tempo de design para o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> em um designer visual.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class documentation.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> documentação de classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] internamente constrói uma nova instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerProxyDesigner> classe quando ele cria associado <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> controle ou uma cópia desse controle na superfície de design.

trans-unit.source: Returns the HTML markup that represents the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a marcação HTML que representa o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the markup that is used to render the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> at design time.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém a marcação que é usada para renderizar o <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: Override this method to change the generated HTML of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Substitua este método para alterar o código HTML gerado do <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> controle em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> component that implements the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: Um componente <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> que implementa a interface <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" />.
